OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNoise row ends 200-year    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fringing of church bell     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A church bell that sounded every hour  
OL,6, for more than 200 years has been       
OL,7, silenced after a noise complaint.      
OL,9,FThe 24-hour ringing at Beith Parish    
OL,10,FChurch in Ayrshire was stopped after a 
OL,11,Fresident told council environmental    
OL,12,Fhealth their sleep had been disturbed. 
OL,14,FThe Church of Scotland has now stopped 
OL,15,Fthe bell between 23:00 and 07:00.      
OL,17,FA petition to restore the 24-hour chime
OL,18,Fhas gathered more than 900 signatures. 
OL,19,FOrganisers say the tradition is part of
OL,20,Fthe Beith's "history and heritage".    
